Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper investigates autonomic management in a distributed storage system. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper deals with the management of data in a distributed system. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper applies autonomic management to a system. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is a potential category as the paper deals with a peer-to-peer (P2P) system. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also a possible category as the paper develops a generic autonomic management framework.
